dBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-02T17:50:21.000Z","msg":"sor我打呢篇嘢可能激動得制，<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n其實講咁多都係想多啲人響應罷工，再次為我嘅激動講多次對唔住先。"},{"pid":"17d3a2470ac4bcf7dd65c7f1d027ea3c5f0d424e","tid":1689262,"uid":169074,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-02T17:51:52.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"b3d56edb2c4949c55b0fad5d9bef0f8f2bde9677","tid":1689262,"uid":77461,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6dc18e9cad8959638ff43969ac3954cdd33e0d6e","tid":1689262,"uid":195832,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"14c4b7217432db807a036acaf9b57d71cfcc4956","tid":1689262,"uid":77461,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-02T17:45:49.000Z","msg":"叫人罷工真係唔係咁易 叫人AL一日相信仲行得通<br />\n唔好一尾屌人唔罷工 罷工每個人既代價唔同<br />\n<br />\n樓主放學返屋企有飯野 伸手有零用錢<br />\n有班人一早俾人揸住春袋 冇左經濟 根本連飯都冇得食"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-02T17:50:21.000Z","msg":"sor我打呢篇嘢可能激動得制，<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n其實講咁多都係想多啲人響應罷工，再次為我嘅激動講多次對唔住先。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-02T17:53:07.000Z","msg":"我冇質疑你個方向 三罷係有用 <br />\n只係大家千期唔好指責唔罷工既同路人"},{"pid":"24d2b4a788132c647c521c56ef3c8d8aa43c7963","tid":1689262,"uid":81113,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-05T09:59:58.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"4b861461327ac284eedf11356c248d2112cbbee5","tid":1689262,"uid":59608,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-05T10:01:08.000Z","msg":"如果公司一半人罷<br />\n<br />\n我會跟"},{"pid":"6070a8b1a069d867474b21ec5714b79aa56f919e","tid":1689262,"uid":195832,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4b861461327ac284eedf11356c248d2112cbbee5","tid":1689262,"uid":59608,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-05T10:01:08.000Z","msg":"如果公司一半人罷<br />\n<br />\n我會跟"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-05T14:46:11.000Z","msg":"好想快啲有真三罷"}]}